OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fracist abuse on London     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftrain                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A BBC radio presenter has spoken about 
OL,6, how a group of men directed "racist and
OL,7, misogynistic abuse at multiple         
OL,8, passengers" on a train in south London.
OL,10,FMary Mandefield was on a train from    
OL,11,FBedford to Three Bridges on Thursday   
OL,12,Fnight when she said the men joined the 
OL,13,Ftrain in pursuit of another passenger. 
OL,15,FThe group then got into several        
OL,16,Fphysical fights and started hurling    
OL,17,Fabuse at passengers, she said.         
OL,19,FBritish Transport Police said they are 
OL,20,Finvestigating the incident.            
